description:
ANNA SITKINA

The Russian model and content creator known for her film and TV-inspired photos of her, as well as her striking long red hair and ethereal appearance, is also called Little Bruke. She gained widespread recognition in 2021 after appearing on the cover of Moveux magazine, a significant milestone for her career.

Little Bruke has amassed a large following on her Instagram account, where she regularly posts captivating and unique photos of herself, with over 1.1 million followers to date. Her content is a mix of fashion, beauty, and art, often drawing inspiration from iconic movies and TV shows, and her unique style has earned her a dedicated fan base.

If you enjoy my work and would like to support me, I would greatly appreciate it if you could buy me a beer!
